Record Class Lead

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
net.tangly.erp.crm.domain.Lead
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.tangly.core.HasDate
public record Lead(@NotNull LocalDate date, @NotNull LeadCode code, String firstname, @NotNull String lastname, net.tangly.core.crm.GenderCode gender, String company, net.tangly.core.PhoneNr phoneNr, net.tangly.core.EmailAddress email, String linkedIn, @NotNull ActivityCode activity, String text) extends Record implements net.tangly.core.HasDate
Defines a lead in the customer relation domain. A lead is also often called a prospect. Once a lead was contacted it should either be qualified and integrated into an interaction or disqualified. Leads are persisted to keep track of the disquaified ones over time.
